{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.15.1515;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\sa195\cf1\b\f0\fs20 When you receive and XML file, it will not necessarily be correctly formed. XML files can have a variety of errors, but fortunately they can be validated using the Schema file.\par
This example shows how to use Magic to validated an XML file, using its Schema file.\par
Press the Validate XML button, and the XML file will be validated using Magic functions. Error messages will appear in the subform. You can use the \cf2 Edit Raw XML \cf1 button to introduce some errors into the XML, if you want.\par
